{"tid":1991623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【安全漏洞】中大 Zoom 考試被駭客入侵　學生被逼睇 AV","createTime":"2020-04-27T14:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T14:51:05.000Z","uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1f7fadb63cb3ee7c61c28d173004b11957189a","tid":1991623,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T14:11:43.000Z","msg":"疫情下，多間大專院校均以遙距形式上課以至考試，但通訊軟件 Zoom 的安全性一再受質疑，今早更發生有大學生在考試時被人入侵 Zoom，甚至在聊天室內發布色情資訊的情況。有學生指事情嚴重影響考試心情，中大則表示跟進中。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今早，中大通識課程的考試期間，有學生指考試開始後約 10 分鐘，聊天室內多了幾名不同國籍人士⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7-zoom-%E8%80%83%E8%A9%A6%E8%A2%AB%E9%A7%AD%E5%AE%A2%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%BC%E7%9D%87-av/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7-zoom-%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25A7%25AD%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25BE%25B5-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2580%25BC%25E7%259D%2587-av%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4RV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=65f69f7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7-zoom-%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25A7%25AD%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25BE%25B5-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2580%25BC%25E7%259D%2587-av%2F&h=6ce7c896\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7-zoom-%E8%80%83%E8%A9%A6%E8%A2%AB%E9%A7%AD%E5%AE%A2%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%BC%E7%9D%87-av/</a>"},{"pid":"fa4bf2bf489043ae465dcc8cbdef6f15c3184a7a","tid":1991623,"uid":107297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0